statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `nha_nghi` inner join `nhanghi_hinhanh` on `nhanghi_hinhanh`.`nn_id` = `nha_nghi`.`id` inner join `nhanghi_giatien` on `nhanghi_giatien`.`nn_id` = `nha_nghi`.`id` where sqrt(power((ABS(nha_nghi.toado_lat)-21.004722),2)+power((ABS(nha_nghi.toado_lng)-105.8220581),2))*111<3 group by `nhanghi_hinhanh`.`nn_id`, `nhanghi_giatien`.`nn_id`

select *,round(sqrt(power((ABS(nha_nghi.toado_lat)-21.004722),2)+power((ABS(nha_nghi.toado_lng)-105.8220581),2))*111,1) as khoangcach from `nha_nghi` inner join `nhanghi_hinhanh` on `nhanghi_hinhanh`.`nn_id` = `nha_nghi`.`id` inner join `nhanghi_giatien` on `nhanghi_giatien`.`nn_id` = `nha_nghi`.`id` where sqrt(power((ABS(nha_nghi.toado_lat)-21.004722),2)+power((ABS(nha_nghi.toado_lng)-105.8220581),2))*111<3 group by `nhanghi_hinhanh`.`nn_id`, `nhanghi_giatien`.`nn_id` order by `nhanghi_giatien`.`phongdon_motgio` asc limit 2 offset 0
